    "it allows us to use our natural language, such as English, German, or Spanish, instead of formal languages or code, such as Python or Java.",
    "A new, elusive normal.",
    "Platforms such as ChatGPT are based on so-called Large Language Models (LLMs).",
    "These models are characterized by the fact that interactions with them are not based on predefined text modules or commands, but on written language in all its diversity.",
    "So if you write to systems like ChatGPT in natural language, they can understand you and respond in the same language."
  ]
